{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-428-necklace-of-circles","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 428: Lanac krugova","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Ako $a$, $b$ i $c$ su pozitivni brojevi.</p>\n<p>Ako su $W$, $X$, $Y$, $Z$ četiri tačke na istoj pravoj gde $|WX| = a$, $|XY| = b$, $|YZ| = c$ i $|WZ| = a + b + c$.</p>\n<p>Neka $C_{\\text{in}}$ bude krug sa prečnikom $XY$.</p>\n<p>Neka je $C_{\\text{out}}$ krug sa prečnikom $WZ$.</p>\n<p>Trokut ($a$, $b$, $c$) se naziva <em>lančanični trokutnik</em> ako je moguće postaviti različite kružnice $C_1, C_2, \\ldots, C_k$ na sledeći način:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>$C_i$ nema unutrašnje tačke koje dele sa bilo kojim $C_j$ za $1 ≤ i$, $j ≤ k$ i $i ≠ j$,</li>\n<li>$C_i$ povezuje $C_{\\text{in}}$ sa $C_{\\text{out}}$ za $1 ≤ i ≤ k$,</li>\n<li>$C_i$ povezuje $C_{i + 1}$ za $1 ≤ i &#x3C; k$, i</li>\n<li>$C_k$ povezuje $C_1$.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Na primer, (5, 5, 5) i (4, 3, 21) su lančane trojke, dok se može pokazati da (2, 2, 5) nije.</p>\n<img alt=\"wakilisho wa trojia ya mnyororo\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/necklace-of-circles.png\" style=\"background-color: white; padding: 10px; display: block; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>Neka je $T(n)$ broj trojki u lancetu $(a, b, c)$ gde su $a$, $b$ i $c$ pozitivni ceo brojevi, i $b ≤ n$. Na primer, $T(1) = 9$, $T(20) = 732$ i $T(3\\,000) = 438\\,106$.</p>\n<p>Pronađi $T(1\\,000\\,000\\,000)$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f5191000cf542c51002b","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302098,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-428-necklace-of-circles"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function necklace(n) {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nnecklace(1000000000)","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>necklace(1000000000)</code> trebalo bi da vrati <code>747215561862</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(necklace(1000000000), 747215561862);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-401-to-480","dashedName":"problem-428-necklace-of-circles","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-429-sum-of-squares-of-unitary-divisors","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-427-n-sequences","id":"5900f5191000cf542c51002b","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-428-necklace-of-circles"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}